@startuml SD_12_VoucherManagement
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Voucher Management
' FR-33~FR-36: Create Voucher + Validate at Checkout
' ============================================================

title **SD-12: Voucher Management\n(Create → Validate → Apply Discount)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
    ParticipantBorderColor #F9A825
    ArrowColor #F9A825
}

actor "Organizer /\nAdmin" as Creator #Gold
participant "Browser" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "VoucherServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #FFFDE7
participant "VoucherService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "VoucherDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5
actor "Attendee" as Customer #LightBlue

== Part A: Create Voucher ==

Creator -> Browser: Open Voucher Management
Browser -> Controller: GET /organizer/vouchers
activate Controller
Controller --> Browser: Forward → vouchers.jsp\n(list + create form)
deactivate Controller

Creator -> Browser: Fill in voucher info:\ncode: "SUMMER2025"\ntype: percentage\nvalue: 10%\nmaxDiscount: 200,000 VND\nminOrderAmount: 500,000 VND\nusageLimit: 100\nstartDate, endDate
Browser -> Controller: POST /organizer/vouchers/create\n{code, discountType,\ndiscountValue, maxDiscount,\nminOrderAmount, usageLimit,\nstartDate, endDate, eventId}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: createVoucher(voucherData)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: findByCode("SUMMER2025")
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Vouchers\nWHERE code = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: null (not exists)
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: null
deactivate DAO

alt #FFE0E0 Code Already Exists
    Service --> Controller: "Voucher code already exists"
    Controller --> Browser: Error
else #E8F5E9 Code Available

    Service -> DAO: create(voucher)
    activate DAO
    DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO Vouchers (\n  voucherId, code, discountType,\n  discountValue, maxDiscount,\n  minOrderAmount, usageLimit,\n  usedCount=0, startDate, endDate,\n  scope='EVENT', eventId,\n  fundSource='ORGANIZER',\n  isActive=1, createdAt\n)
    activate DB
    DB --> DAO: Created
    deactivate DB
    DAO --> Service: voucher
    deactivate DAO

    Service --> Controller: voucher
    deactivate Service
    Controller --> Browser: Redirect + flash:\n"Voucher created successfully"
    deactivate Controller
    Browser --> Creator: ✅ Voucher SUMMER2025 created
end

== Part B: Apply Voucher at Checkout ==

Customer -> Browser: Enter voucher "SUMMER2025"\nat checkout
Browser -> Controller: POST /checkout/validate-voucher\n{code: "SUMMER2025",\ntotalAmount: 1600000,\neventId}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: validateVoucher(\n"SUMMER2025", 1600000, eventId)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: findByCode("SUMMER2025")
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Vouchers\nWHERE code = 'SUMMER2025'
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Voucher
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: voucher
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: **Validate 7 conditions:**\n1. ✅ Code exists\n2. ✅ isActive == true\n3. ✅ now ≥ startDate\n4. ✅ now ≤ endDate\n5. ✅ usedCount (50) < usageLimit (100)\n6. ✅ totalAmount (1.6M) ≥ minOrder (500K)\n7. ✅ scope (EVENT) matches event

alt #FFE0E0 Validation Failed
    Service --> Controller: {valid: false,\nerror: "Voucher has expired"}
    Controller --> Browser: JSON {valid: false,\nmessage: "Voucher has expired"}
    Browser --> Customer: ❌ Invalid voucher
else #E8F5E9 Valid!

    Service -> Service: **Calculate discount:**\ntype: percentage (10%)\ndiscount = 1,600,000 × 10%\n= 160,000 VND\nmaxDiscount = 200,000\nfinalDiscount = min(160K, 200K)\n= **160,000 VND**

    Service --> Controller: {valid: true,\ndiscountAmount: 160000,\nnewTotal: 1440000}
    deactivate Service

    Controller --> Browser: JSON {valid: true,\ndiscount: "160,000 VND",\nnewTotal: "1,440,000 VND"}
    deactivate Controller

    Browser -> Browser: Update checkout UI:\n-160,000 VND discount\nTotal: 1,440,000 VND
    Browser --> Customer: ✅ Voucher applied!\nDiscount: 160,000 VND
end

@enduml
